    "GPU clusters generally provide services for parallel tenants.",
    "Multi-user GPU clusters are usually managed by the cluster manager (Hindman et al., 2011; Vavilapalli et al., 2013; Wu et al., 2021) or the GPU cluster customized scheduler (Peng et al., 2018; Xiao et al., 2018; Gu et al., 2019; Mahajan et al., 2020).",
